divs: Sighting DetailsI did not witness the event. I read it in our local paper; The Valley Citizen, November 9, 2011 edition, Volume III, Issue 45. Hope Strong wrote the story ahout a local rancher who found his cow dead and mutilated on November 3, 2011, in a wheat field about 6 miles south of Driggs, Idaho. You can read the story on Valley Citizen's Facebook page.
Summary: Mutilated Cow found by rancher south of Driggs, Idaho
trends: There have been no other sightings in Driggs
This sighting has never been favorited.
